so text decoration parameters change the style of the a row's text based on the corresponding record attribute

syntaxx: 
decoration-name .  
and it is put inside of the view,
<tree decoration-info="field and condition state">
<tree decoration-info="state=='draft'></tree>
<form decoration-info="age&lt;5"/> if age is less or equal than 5 change the color to info decorator 
<kanban decoration-info="field="
the name refers to a color 

decoration-danger
decoration-info
decoration-muted
decoration-primary
decoration-success
decoration-warning


decoration-bf : font-weight: bold
decoration-it : font-weight: italic

there's editable option

